PATHOLOGY IMAGE OF THE MONTH. Autopsy Findings in an Adult with Down Syndrome.

Connor EE(1), Darga A(2), McGoey RR(3).

Author information:
(1)Second-year Pathology Resident in the Department of Pathology at Louisiana 
State University's School of Medicine in New Orleans.
(2)Third-year Pathology Resident in the Department of Pathology at Louisiana 
State University's School of Medicine in New Orleans.
(3)Associate Professor of Pathology and Residency Program Director at Louisiana 
