Age stratified comparative analysis of perioperative, functional and oncologic 
outcomes in patients after robot assisted radical prostatectomy--A propensity 
score matched study.

Kumar A(1), Samavedi S(2), Bates AS(2), Giedelman Cuevas CA(2), Coelho RF(2), 
Rocco B(2), Palmer K(2), Patel VR(2).

Author information:
(1)Department of Urology, University of Central Florida College of Medicine and 
Global Robotics Institute, Florida Hospital-Celebration Health, FL, USA. 
Electronic address: anup_14k@yahoo.com.
(2)Department of Urology, University of Central Florida College of Medicine and 
